Flash tools for (unreleased) Tarako b2g device.

Requires access to Mozilla Taipei VPN (sorry).
It will download the images and flash them.

flash_tarako_eng.sh
        Flash engineering build.

flash_tarako.sh
        Flash production build.

flash_gaia_gecko.sh
        Flash gaia + gecko.

shallow_flash.sh
        Helper to flash gaia + gecko.
